{
  "stem": "21731.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] [SIGHS] I still went to this hospital because it was-- this hospital still existed.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Every day, my-- every day, you heard and saw the most-- the most terrible things which you can imagine.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You can't imagine what, what I saw while walking to, to, to my work because Jews were not allowed to use the tram.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And Jews were not allowed to walk on the sidewalk.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We had to walk on the street.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Once I was [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] beaten by a German or Ukrainian soldier because I was-- I wasn't thinking.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I just walked on the sidewalk-- and 'Jude, Jude.'",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, well, he, he-- with his rifle, gave me a good few over my head.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And somebody found me and brought me back home.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was-- then-- but I was alive.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I wasn't dead.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Well, there was-- there was real hunger and especially fear.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I never know whether I will find my mother and Jan at home when I go home.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I left at 5 o'clock in the morning and came back late afternoon or perhaps in the evening.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "In the meantime, sometimes I couldn't even go to the hospital because I was caught by Germans who, who wanted the streets cleaned, the snow cleaned.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The-- it was bitter cold.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I have no, no warm clothes because all-- well, the furs were confiscated at once.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Jews had to give the furs at once.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But I have to go back now, when I talk about furs.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The Judenrat was naturally at once installed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And the Gestapo was asking the Judenrat to give them a thousand fur coats or a thousand [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] watches or a thousand-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I don't know what.",
      "word_count": 33
    }
  ],
